  <h1>Banking & Finance Jobs</h1>

  <p>Banking and finance jobs are among the most stable and respected non-technical career options. They offer long-term growth and security.</p>

  <h2>Popular Roles</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Bank Clerk</li>
    <li>Relationship Manager</li>
    <li>Loan Officer</li>
    <li>Customer Service Officer</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Skills Required</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Numerical ability</li>
    <li>Communication skills</li>
    <li>Attention to detail</li>
    <li>Basic financial knowledge</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why Choose Banking?</h2>
  <p>Banking jobs provide job security, structured career growth, and attractive benefits.</p>

  <h2>Where to Apply</h2>
  <p>Private banks, government exams, NBFCs, and financial institutions regularly hire candidates.</p>

